    [31mThe paint storage or a production area with flammable gas shall be provided with electrical equipment of appropriate Ex category.[39m
    [31mThe power factor correction capacitors should be provided, p.f. should be maintained at 0.9 (lag).[39m
    [31mThe wiring for machines should be preferably carried out using armoured cable or single core wires in GI conduit/ trunking.[39m
    [31mOTHER SERVICES THAT MIGHT BE REQUIRED TO FULFIL CERTAIN CRITERIA[39m
